Sentinel's Neo Caliph Wololo Tank was created/rendered by Thobie Buntaran a.k.a. Loreng on 07 September 2021, Mantrijeron, Yogyakarta, Indonesia.

The Wololo Tank, mainly used for gold, glory, and gospel domination campaign on another habitable planet. A glorious & holy instrument of war made entirely of pure solid gold materials. Claimed to be a weapon of mass destruction from the 3020's, this tank variant can easily destroy its enemies on open battlefields. Mounted with Triple Golden Giant Megaphones as its main weapon to wreak havoc and manipulate the wide range of sound frequencies in long-range combat. During peaceful times, Neo Caliph Wololo Tanks serves as a protector and mobile sound system at the same time.
